                    ]
                ],
                [
                    "description",
                    "ALPHV/BlackCat affiliates use targeted phishing campaigns as an initial access vector, delivering malicious emails crafted to deceive recipients into executing attachments. Successful phishing establishes the first foothold on victim hosts, enabling follow-on loader deployment, credential harvesting, and staging for triple-extortion ransomware operations."
