                        ]
                    ]
                ],
                [
                    "description",
                    "ALPHV/BlackCat affiliates abuse internet-facing RDP endpoints, VPN gateways, Citrix environments, and remote monitoring tools as the central pivot point — authenticating with stolen credentials to bypass perimeter defences. This node anchors all post-access operations: lateral movement, multi-tool deployment, staged data exfiltration, and ultimately the ALPHV encryptor across Windows, Linux, and VMware ESXi environments."
                ],
