                    "description",
                    "Custom ALPHV/BlackCat data-exfiltration tool written in .NET that selectively targets and uploads high-value file types — documents, spreadsheets, databases, and archives — to attacker-controlled SFTP or WebDAV infrastructure. ExMatter prioritises files by extension and size, maximising exfiltration throughput and supporting the group's triple-extortion pressure model."
